FBIS3-51014 "drlat008_a_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 January 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Agreement Signed for Waste Treatment Plant FL1101151194 Havana Radio Progreso Network in Spanish 1200 GMT 11 Jan 94 FL1101151194 Havana Radio Progreso Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The Cuban Government and the common fund for basic products signed a finance agreement for the construction of a plant to treat the residue from factories that produce alcohol from molasses. The installation will be built in areas of the Heriberto Duques Sugar Mill in Villa Clara, at a cost of $3 million.
